summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Fractal Research Terminal application. All core endpoints and UI components are working correctly with bootstrap data loaded (5694 candles).

Admin panel Volatility tab - Regime Timeline and Performance by Regime table
Chart mode switching - Price Chart and Fractal Overlay modes work correctly
Interactive elements - Chart mode buttons are clickable and functional
Data integration - Backend APIs properly integrated with frontend components
